00:14:17,760 --> 00:14:18,560
Dr. Yang, look.

296
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,080
You're right.

297
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:22,920
This kind of metal poisoning

298
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:25,600
is not something we know.

299
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:26,760
Maybe.

300
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,480
They have these symptoms.

301
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:30,080
But we can't detect them.

302
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:31,840
Poisoned?

303
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,480
Someone poisoned my mom.

304
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:35,000
It shouldn't be poisoning.

305
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:36,880
Qiu Ya, calm down.

306
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:38,760
Yang Mo Li.

307
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:40,320
Come and show it to the director.

308
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:41,800
I'm sorry, Qiu Ya.

309
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,040
I'll talk to you later.

310
00:14:43,640 --> 00:14:44,000
It's okay.

311
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:48,000
Dr. Jung.

312
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:49,320
A foreign doctor?

313
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:51,160
Do you have experience and solutions?

314
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:53,040
I want to contact the doctor there.

315
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:54,320
Okay.

316
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:56,120
Here are the test results.

317
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:57,080
Take it and ask.

318
00:14:57,560 --> 00:14:58,080
Thank you.

319
00:14:58,560 --> 00:14:59,680
I'll let you know if there's any news.

320
00:14:59,800 --> 00:15:00,120
Okay.

321
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:02,920
In the ward.

322
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:04,120
You're not my boss.

323
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:05,240
You're just my patient.

324
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:07,640
I told you.

325
00:15:08,160 --> 00:15:09,160
I'm not sick.

326
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,760
I just feel a little dizzy.

327
00:15:11,520 --> 00:15:13,280
It's not a big deal.

328
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:14,600
Maybe hypoglycemia.

329
00:15:14,920 --> 00:15:15,880
It could be brain hemorrhage.

330
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:17,000
Brain infarction, brain...

331
00:15:17,160 --> 00:15:18,600
Okay, stop it.

332
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,800
I'm not sick now.

333
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:22,840
I'm fine now. I want to be discharged.

334
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:23,640
That's impossible.

335
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,600
Your blood test report is abnormal.

336
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:27,320
Tell me the truth.

337
00:15:27,640 --> 00:15:28,920
Did you eat something randomly?

338
00:15:31,160 --> 00:15:32,280
What did you eat?

339
00:15:32,760 --> 00:15:34,640
I'm just too busy at work.

340
00:15:34,800 --> 00:15:35,600
What did you say?

341
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:39,840
My teeth.

342
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:41,560
You didn't tell me the truth even your teeth fell off.

343
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:43,600
The wife of the Finance Minister

344
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:45,320
and Qiu Ya's mother were sent here.

345
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:46,920
One of them has a rotten face.

346
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,800
And the other one is in pain.

347
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:49,480
What?

348
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:50,920
Mrs. Sun also...

349
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:54,040
Oh no.

350
00:15:54,520 --> 00:15:55,840
I'm in trouble now.

351
00:15:59,040 --> 00:15:59,520
I...

352
00:16:02,040 --> 00:16:03,600
I took the Restoration Pill.
